ogramme Analyst, Pov- erty and Inclusion, UNDP Nepal \u2022 Archana Aryal, Team Leader, Democratic Transition Unit, UNDP Nepal New Zealand Mike Reid Local Government New Zealand (LGNZ) \u2022 Brian Roberts, Director, Urban Frontiers/ Emeritus Professor, University of Canberra Pakistan Anwar Hussain Local Councils Association of the Punjab (LCAP) \u2022 Said Rehman, Department of Local Govern- ment, Elections and Rural Development, Go Khyber Pakhtunkhwa \u2022 Masood Ul Mulk, Chief Executive Officer, Sarhad Rural Support Program, Peshawar, Khyber Pakhtunkhwa \u2022 Anwar Hussain, Director, Local Council Board, LCAP \u2022 Amer Ejaz, Executive Director, Centre for Peace and Development Initiative, Punjab Philippines Gail Pamintuan and M. Veronica Hitosis (League of Cities of the Philippines) \u2022 Mia Quimpo, National President, Philippine Institute of Environmental Planners \u2022 Melissa Navarra, Presidential Commission for the Urban Poor \u2022 Christopher E. Rollo, Country Programme Manager, UN-Habitat Philippines \u2022 Raemond Angelo G. Karagdag, Secretariat and Environmental Planner, Philippine In- stitute of Environmental Planners \u2022 Fe Cabral, Programme Analyst, Democratic Governance, UNDP Philippines \u2022 Cleto Gales, Governance Specialist, Demo- cratic Governance, UNDP Philippines Solomon Islands Freddie Jones (Honiara City Clerk) \u2022 Brenda Joy Wara, European Union Delega- tion to Solomon Islands and Vanuatu \u2022 Alan McNeal, Adviser, Australia Department of Foreign Affairs and Trade South Korea Kwi-Gon Kim (Seoul National University/International Urban Training", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "5f88733b-4ab1-425d-ad13-5ba9f0be4630": {"__data__": {"id_": "5f88733b-4ab1-425d-ad13-5ba9f0be4630", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/city-enabling